summary: An ordinance accepting a deed from Chevra Bikur Cholum, a Washington corporation, to the west 30 feet of the east one-half of the southwest one-quarter of the northeast one-quarter of Section 30, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W. M., and other properties, for street purposes; laying off Stone Avenue and the intersection of North 120th Street and Ashworth Avenue, and establishing grades for Stone Avenue.
